These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: american, australian, german, japanese, malaysian, mexican, polish
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, milk, lemonade, cola, almond-milk, soy-milk
 1. the american is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 2. the german is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 3. the polish is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
 5. the australian is somewhere to the right of the american##5
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the japanese##1
 7. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the polish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
11. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
12. the malaysian is on the left of the mexican##1
13. the mexican is in the middle##1
14. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the german##5
15. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
16. the person drinking cola is not the polish##6
17. the american is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
18. the person drinking mirinda is not the german##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | american | japanese | malaysian | mexican | polish | german | australian |
| Pet           | lemonade   | almond-milk    | soy-milk       | coffee     | milk    | cola   | mirinda |

