 1. the german is not the alhambra-smoker##6
 2. the japanese is not the alhambra-smoker##6
 3. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the french##1
 5. the french is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 6. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 7. the australian is on the left of the japanese##1
 8. the german is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
 9. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
10. the japanese is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is not the french##6
12. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
13. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
14. the bolivar-smoker is the malaysian##1
15. the japanese is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
16. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
17. the french is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
18. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
19. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
20. the havana-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
21. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5

