 3. the owner of the fish is not the japanese##6
 4. the owner of the fish is not the polish##6
 5. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
 6. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the polish is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 8. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
 9. the polish is on the left or right of the canadian##3
10. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
11. the american is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
12. the chinese is on the far right##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the chinese##1
14. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the american##3
15. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
16. the polish is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5

