 3. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 4. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the person eating pear is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
 6. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5
 7. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person eating banana##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is in the middle##1
11. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
12. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
13. the person traveling to colone is not the person eating cauliflower##6
14. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
15. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
16. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person eating nectarine##5
18. the person eating pear is not the person traveling to edinburgh##6
19. the person eating pear is between the person eating nectarine and the person traveling to hannover##2
