.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-7::.
7 different pets are kept: bird, frog, goat, guinea-pig, hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: june, january, may, october, november, april, july
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 2. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 4. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 6. the owner of the hamster is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the goat is the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
13. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
14. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
15. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
16. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |  7   |
