 1. the person eating pumpkin is the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 3. the person playing chess is not the person eating apricot##6
 4. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the person eating cherry is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
 6. the person eating cherry is the person playing monopoly##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
 9. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
10. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person playing chess##1
12. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person eating garlic##5
13. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
